rows.label: tlk41100124_06_msg0001
rows.name:
You... You're the one who beat my
high score in Tiger! Tiger!, aren't you?

rows.label: tlk41100124_06_msg0002
rows.name:
I thought nobody would ever be able
to beat my 81,107 points...

rows.label: tlk41100124_06_msg0003
rows.name:
You're too good. I admit defeat.
I guess there's always someone
stronger out there somewhere.

rows.label: tlk41100124_06_msg0004
rows.name:
I don't think I'll be able to get a score
higher than that again. I think it's time
I moved on from Tiger! Tiger!, yes.

rows.label: tlk41100124_06_msg0005
rows.name:
I want you to have this, for being
such a fantastic rival.

rows.label: tlk41100124_06_msg0101
rows.name:
My dream was to go to Superbia and
become a botanical scientist...

rows.label: tlk41100124_06_msg0102
rows.name: But I've found a new dream now.

rows.label: tlk41100124_06_msg0103
rows.name:
I'm going to make a game even more
exciting than Tiger! Tiger! ever was!

rows.label: tlk41100124_06_msg0104
rows.name:
And someday, when I finish it,
I'll challenge you to beat me at it.
